                <head>No. 283.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cushing</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-09-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 29, 1875</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Telegraph of twenty-eighth received; shall I take new steps on it at once, or
                    wait for specific instructions on my numbers four eighty-seven, four ninety-two,
                    and five hundred one?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>CUSHING.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
